snippet.title: Octarina 0.0.5 Trailer
snippet.description:
Octarina is a physics-based Octopus game, where the main gameplay features are the control of the octopus and the interaction with the environment.

You can wishlist the game on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1503280/Octarina/

If you want to be part of the community, feel free to join our discord! 
https://discord.gg/DMUrRRr

For updates and more sneak peeks follow us on social media.
https://twitter.com/octarina_game
https://www.instagram.com/octarina_game
